---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { SITE } from "../data/site";
---

<BaseLayout
  meta={{
    title: "Privacy Policy",
    description: "Privacy policy for breachwalker.com and the Breachwalker closed alpha.",
    path: "/privacy",
  }}
>
  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="muted">Last updated: {SITE.legalUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <article class="container container--narrow prose">
    <p>
      This policy describes how Breachwalker, a production of{" "}
      <a href={SITE.producer.url}>{SITE.producer.name}</a> (“we”, “us”),
      collects and uses information when you visit{" "}
      <a href={SITE.url}>breachwalker.com</a> or sign up for the closed alpha.
    </p>

    <h2>Information we collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Alpha signup:</strong> email address and optional Discord handle
        when you submit the waitlist form.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Analytics:</strong> aggregated page views, referrers, country,
        and device type via Cloudflare Web Analytics (no advertising cookies in
        the default configuration).
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Contact:</strong> information you send us by email.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How we use information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Send alpha invitations and product updates you opt into.</li>
      <li>Understand site traffic and improve the marketing site.</li>
      <li>Respond to support requests.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third parties</h2>
    <p>We use service providers that process data on our behalf:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Cloudflare</strong> — hosting, DNS, and web analytics.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Tally</strong> (or similar form provider) — alpha signup form
        hosting, if enabled.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not sell your personal information.</p>

    <h2>Retention</h2>
    <p>
      Alpha signup data is kept until you unsubscribe, we close the waitlist, or
      a reasonable period after the alpha ends — whichever comes first. Analytics
      data is retained according to our analytics provider’s policies.
    </p>

    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>
      Depending on where you live, you may have rights to access, correct, or
      delete your personal data. Contact us at
      <a href={`mailto:${SITE.privacyEmail}`}>{SITE.privacyEmail}</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Children</h2>
    <p>
      Breachwalker is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly
      collect data from children.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this policy. The “Last updated” date at the top will change
      when we do.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions: <a href={`mailto:${SITE.privacyEmail}`}>{SITE.privacyEmail}</a>
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
